as forays into Fresh-Air Coolers; and launches ‘All-Weather Smart’ AC range</a></h4><p class="card-text">Voltas Limited, India’s leading room air conditioner brand, today announced the launch of Voltas Fresh‐Air Coolers. The new range comes with attractive features such as exclusive honeycomb cooling pads, carbonised dust filters and powerful air throw.</p><h6 class="card-overtitle">May 2015, Mumbai</h6><a href="https://devvoltas.voltasworld.com/images/publications/May_05%2C_2015_Voltas_forays_into_Fresh-Air_Coolers.pdf" class="press-download"><i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i> <span class="">download pdf</span></a></div></div></div>      <div class="col-12 all financial"><div class="card voltas-card voltas-card-press_release"><div class="card-body"><h4 class="card-title"><a href="https://devvoltas.voltasworld.com/images/publications/February_11%2C_2015_Voltas%E2%80%99_Q3_Consolidated_Financial_Results_for_2014-15.pdf_.pdf" target="_blank">Voltas’ Q3 Consolidated Financial Results for 2014-15</a></h4><p class="card-text">The Consolidated SaleslIncome from Operations for the nine months period ended 31st December, 2014 was ~ 3660 crores as compared to ~ 3793 crores in the corresponding period last year. Profit from Operations before Other Income, Finance Costs and Exceptional items was however significantly higher at ~ 247 crores as compared to ~ 142 crores in the corresponding period last year.</p><h6 class="card-overtitle">February 2015, Mumbai</h6><a href="https://devvoltas.voltasworld.com/images/publications/February_11%2C_2015_Voltas%E2%80%99_Q3_Consolidated_Financial_Results_for_2014-15.pdf_.pdf" class="press-download"><i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i> <span class="">download pdf</span></a></div></div></div>  </div></div></div>  ";}